I feel disappointed because my precious 2 experiences were so good. But the fly situation is concerning. Something must be wrong in the kitchen. I shan’t be returning here ever again. I hope that the owners deals with the flies and probably disgusting kitchen/rotting food situation. ——————————————————————— My original review: My first time at Anatolia was excellent.
